<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="./images/icons8-read-96.png" />
    <!--google fonts-->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Righteous&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <!--search bar icon-->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/QnA.css" />
    <!-- //*Footer  -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://demos.creative-tim.com/notus-js/assets/styles/tailwind.css"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://demos.creative-tim.com/notus-js/assets/vendor/@fortawesome/fontawesome-free/css/all.min.css"
    />
    <!-- //*Font awsome  -->
    <script
      src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/53405766b0.js"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <title>TechJoy || FAQ</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('./nav'); -%>

    <!--top picture and its content-->
    <div class="question-picture">
      <img src="./images/undraw_faq_re_31cw.svg" alt="" />
      <div class="image-content-container">
        <h1>welcome to tech<span>joy</span></h1>
        <p>here you well find answers to our frequently asked questions</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!--questions-->
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      <div class="accordion">
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button id="accordion-button-1" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="accordion-title">Who we are ?</span
            ><span class="icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>
              We are a group of three passionate developers from morocco
              dedicated to learning new technologies and providing the best user
              experience on our services for people to enjoy.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button id="accordion-button-5" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="accordion-title">Are we open for hire ?</span
            ><span class="icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>
              Yes we are open for hire, We can help you in developing your next
              idea and making it a fully functional website as you please, or
              for consulting opportunities, for more in-depth information
              contact us in our personal email : zaydinani@protonmail.com
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button id="accordion-button-2" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="accordion-title">What to expect from this blog ?</span
            ><span class="icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>
              In this blog, you will go with us on our journey as we learn more
              about coding since we will be sharing our progress with you
              through this blog, and also we will be sharing more information
              that we find interesting about tech in general.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button id="accordion-button-3" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="accordion-title">Why we started this blog ?</span
            ><span class="icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>
              we started this blog to test our knowledge of coding and to show
              our skills to the world as we progress even more.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button id="accordion-button-4" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="accordion-title"
              >can you use our articles or things we share in this blog ?</span
            ><span class="icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>
              Yes you can use our articles or any of the other information we
              will be sharing on this blog, But we will appreciate if you give
              us credit by writing where you got this information from.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button id="accordion-button-5" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="accordion-title">how we made this blog ?</span
            ><span class="icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>
              we made this blog using many languages such as HTML, CSS3, and
              JavaScript for front-end together with node.js and express.js for
              back-end as well as mySQL for the database.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!--contact us -->
    <div class="contact">
      <p>if your questions are not answered above make sure to contact us</p>
      <button class="btn"><a href="./contact">contact us</a></button>
    </div>
    <%- include('./footer'); -%>

    <script defer src="./JavaScript/QnA.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
